Delicious, subtle but tangy. I have a couple of suggestions, though: I think the amount of gelatin is incorrect-I think the amount should be 1 1/2 envelopes, not teaspoons, of gelatin. This amounts to 3 3/4 tsp. I excluded the caramel the second time I made these, and added 1 1/2 tsp balsamic vinegar to the berries.

